    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows two blocks on a ramp. The ramp curves downward and to the right until it reaches a section where it is flat. Block 1 of mass m sub 1 is at the top of a ramp, a vertical height of h sub 0 from the flat section. Block 2 of mass m sub 2 is at the bottom of the ramp, on the flat section.\" src=\"/images/0c0a8b087daee412b46104eeda056ede.svg\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Block <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> of mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m sub 1\"><math alttext=\"m sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span> is released from rest at the top of a ramp of height <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"h sub 0\"><math alttext=\"h sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>h</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span>, as shown. The block slides down the ramp onto a flat section and then collides and sticks to a second block of mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m sub 2\"><math alttext=\"m sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span>, where <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m sub 2 equals m sub 1\"><math alttext=\"m sub 2 equals m sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span>. After the collision, the blocks have speed <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"v sub f\"><math alttext=\"v sub f\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>v</mi><mi>f</mi></msub></math></span></span>. Frictional forces between the blocks and the surface are negligible. Block <